{"tid":876301,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"所有九十後對online game有愛嘅同我入哂嚟","createTime":"2018-10-25T13:53:18.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-01T18:47:47.000Z","uid":143382,"like":12,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"6deee3faee4dd70da4efafef351fc41a69abae46","tid":876301,"uid":143382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T13:53:18.000Z","msg":"呢幾日三小俠（永恆冒險）出咗手機版，令我對小學玩過嘅online game有感想<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n小學開始接觸到online game嘅心情仲記得好清楚，個陣翻學見到同學拎住本個陣好興嘅20蚊本coco個啲前半介紹game同玩具，後半就係危險爺爺吖衰仔擦膠個啲漫畫。我仲記得本野叫天馬行空，廿蚊本有野睇仲送埋隻game碟覺得好抵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，所以就放學去咗報紙灘買。翻到屋企就張隻碟入咗電腦，開始咗我人生第一隻online game，三小俠。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nGame入面所有野都好吸引，我擺好多心機落去要升lv嘅人物到，幾lv買咩裝，點樣唔夠錢所以要skip裝嚟買裝。轉職又係練成為hardcore玩家，同一關打百幾次去打碎片，pvp大家有共識去一人贏一場，當然啦 有啲係贏完就走場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n更新又係當年令我好期待嘅一環<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  十二點放完學（半就班），更新通常要到三點先有得玩，就令我等到好痛苦，但每次一更新完都好想知佢有咩新野。 <br />\n出新職業？<br />\n定出新關卡？<br />\n定係節日限定地圖？<br />\n每樣野都令我好興奮 <br />\n<br />\n比如三小俠出卡查伊斯，出新大陸，出拉思，出萊恩，出真，出Amy，出四轉 <br />\n楓之谷出海盜，出皇家騎士團，出新旅行地圖<br />\n跑online就出軒少，出dr hell，出農場，出獅身人面像<br />\n<br />\n全部喺十幾年後我仲記得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n仲有同人交流嘅部分，大家係刷副本或者打怪升lv打到麻目嘅時候會交流一兩句，又或者有啲啱啱入game新手唔識路，向你問路或者問你畀錢，又或者大家交易個陣講下價，都令我好窩心，就算隔住個mon都feel到人情味<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/25/214918_8ec8065c6bdbb4906aaeabe826d2bb50.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F25%2F214918_8ec8065c6bdbb4906aaeabe826d2bb50.png&h=f43e798d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/25/214931_513a225d10d21557803473fe01e3a02c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F25%2F214931_513a225d10d21557803473fe01e3a02c.png&h=6b349544&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n最後呢到係我為左拉思<br />\n當年買咗隻碟，keep到宜家。隻碟十幾年前98蚊好貴，多謝吖哥買畀我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<br />\n宜家全部舊時online game出手機game都冇玩，唔想破壞童年幻想<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6d10991363b3e66defae324e1ac3d3bb6863d86","tid":876301,"uid":79077,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T13:54:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e3990b7e3f8c0573852bd556dca3d9caa1ce51dd","tid":876301,"uid":143382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e6d10991363b3e66defae324e1ac3d3bb6863d86","tid":876301,"uid":79077,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T13:54:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T13:57:55.000Z","msg":"巴打當年玩咩驚"},{"pid":"3b84e9cffc0eb01c3edf50a707dedf91082cda1e","tid":876301,"uid":130177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T14:17:21.000Z","msg":"港服轉職任難解到on 9 唔課唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n都要抽魔珠裝"},{"pid":"2c4b69ef20a4f46fec530cda603ee589e92a8702","tid":876301,"uid":76323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T14:34:51.000Z","msg":"+1 <br />\n前日down左手機板 入場聽到首ost 仲要係韓版<br />\n聽左幾粒音D回憶上返哂黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6d9cd84fe1eb58ed4fdad636ec586e94386a080","tid":876301,"uid":76692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T14:36:15.000Z","msg":"三小俠真係好撚正<br />\n<br />\n不過而家隻手機版就不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88334ea3e3d2a0e1565925a3c5a0dbf628a15c8c","tid":876301,"uid":79077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T02:14:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"31a9c674e7ad9241e9ae7e598632a54acb48adb9","tid":876301,"uid":55179,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T18:47:47.000Z","msg":"等緊LFO出手游<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n呢隻D人設故事咁完美 出手游一定多人玩"}]}